\F[beni_angry2]Akane: "Shion-sensei is with Yui... Let's take a detour! We

\F[beni_angry2]Akane: "Yui is with Shion-sensei... Let's take a detour! We

\FF[ringo_smile]Ringo: "Suzaku-san~! Where are you hurrying off to? I have
something I want to request from the detective club?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ringo_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "I can't deal with that now! Can't you see I'm in a
hurry...?"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ringo_smile]\AA[2]Ringo: "Of course♪ It's an emergency. My stalker showed
up..."

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ringo_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Then go to the police! Like Seiryu-san's sister or
someone!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ringo_smile]\AA[2]Ringo: "Eeh~! You're so cold~! Be more sympathetic and
listen to my problem~!!"

\F[beni_angry2]\FF[ringo_smile]\AA[1]Akane: "Gah! Show your true colors! I know that Ringo-san
has fallen, so any more is pointless!"

\FF[ringo_reverse]Ringo: "Seriously!? What the~! If you knew, you should've
said so earlier~!! I was trying so hard~!!"

\FF[ringo_reverse]Ringo: "I turned the tables on my stalker, drained him dry
until there was no seed left! Kyahaha!! So I'm not troubled
at all!!"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ringo_reverse]\AA[1]Akane: "You're insane...! That's awful..."

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ringo_reverse]\AA[2]Ringo: "The stalker must be satisfied, right~! After all, he
got to bang-bang with me♪"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ringo_reverse]\AA[2]Ringo: "Whoops... Just thinking about it makes me wanna do
it again~♪"

\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ringo_reverse]\AA[2]Ringo: "Kihhihih♪ I wonder if there's even a dribble left?
Let's test it out~!"
\F[beni_trouble]\FF[ringo_reverse]\AA[1]Akane: "Gah..."
\F[beni_damage]Akane: "Anyway, we need to get away!!"
